The model estimates were derived with  a) detailed global seabird population data collated from a large number of sources (data sources date from 1980-2010 for different parts of the world) b) climate data (source: High-resolution Gridded Datasets, Climatic Research Unit, University of East Anglia, UK.  http://www.cru.uea.ac.uk/cru/data/hrg/ last updated by Harris, I. (2007), date: 1995) c) emission model derived by Riddick et al. (2012) with funding for the project from the CEH Integrating Fund (NERC).  A detailed description and discussion of the datasets, including methodology and uncertainties, can be found in the following peer-reviewed article:   S. N. Riddick, U. Dragosits, T. D. Blackall, F. Daunt, S. Wanless and M. A. Sutton (2012) The global distribution of ammonia emissions from seabird colonies. Atmospheric Environment, 55 (2012), pp. 319-327 DOI: 10.1016/j.atmosenv.2012.02.052</dcterms:description>         <dcterms:issued rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-04-10T09:30:00Z</dcterms:issued>         <dcterms:modified rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-06-13T08:43:29Z</dcterms:modified>         <documentcontainer:catalogLink>http://data.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/c9e802b3-43c8-4b36-a3a3-8861d9da8ea9</documentcontainer:catalogLink>         <dcterms:title xml:lang="en">Global ammonia emissions from seabirds</dcterms:title>         <dcterms:created rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-03-07T16:12:37Z</dcterms:created>         <documentcontainer:id xml:lang="en">c9e802b3-43c8-4b36-a3a3-8861d9da8ea9</documentcontainer:id>         <dcterms:creator>leav</dcterms:creator>       </documentcontainer:documentContainer>     </dcterms:isPartOf>     <file:id xml:lang="en">global-ammonia-emissions-from-seabirds-supporting-information</file:id>     <dcterms:modified rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-03-12T15:09:43Z</dcterms:modified>     <dcterms:title xml:lang="en">Global Ammonia Emissions from Seabirds - Supporting Information</dcterms:title>     <dcterms:created rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2012-03-12T15:09:43Z</dcterms:created>     <dcterms:creator>leav</dcterms:creator>   </file:File> </rdf:RDF>
